      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you're feeling very isolated right now, and that sense of invisibility can be incredibly heavy to carry. Please know that even though you feel unseen, your presence matters deeply to the people around you, even if it doesn't feel like it. If these thoughts of disappearing become overwhelming, reaching out to a trusted friend or a mental health professional can provide the support you need. You are not a ghost; you are a real person deserving of care and attention.",
