      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't think it's a distortion though. it's just math. one person out of billions, in a city where i'm a total stranger... the math doesn't add up to anything significant. it's almost peaceful thinking about it, though. the idea that i could just slip away and there wouldn't be this huge, dramatic hole left behind. just a quiet, seamless exit. like i was never part of the equation at all.",
