      "content": "Those feelings of relief and detachment are dangerous signs that you are losing touch with the reality of your own existence. While the math might seem to support your point, the human experience is far more interconnected than simple statistics suggest, and your pain is real even if you can't see it. Please consider that this \"peaceful\" mindset is a symptom of severe depression rather than a logical conclusion, and you deserve support to navigate through this darkness. If you can, reach out to a crisis helpline or a therapist who can help you find the strength to stay and find meaning in your life.",
